title: Deer Dress
description:
The Deer Dress is a dreamy fawn design, made of custom-printed velveteen to mimic the texture of a deer's fur. Featuring embroidered antlers on a Peter Pan collar, a removable waist bow which can be positioned in any direction, and pockets. The contrast sleeves have beautiful embroidered details and a lace inset.

A long row of functional buttons creates the center front opening, lined with lace. These buttons are placed closely together to prevent gaping. The velveteen body, contrast sleeves, decorative lace, and lining are all 100% cotton.

Each dress comes with a matching hair bow with a barrette clip on the back.

Wear it with or without a petticoat for your desired silhouette. This dress is photographed with a petticoat (not included).

Brand: Atelier Heidi
Materials: 100% cotton. Made in China.
Care: machine wash cold, tumble dry low or hang to dry

title: 'Spookygotchi' Comfy Dress
description:
Our original printed series called ‘Spookygotchi’. The print is drawn by our amazing Antygea and it’s exclusive for Lady Sloth. The comfy dress is made from the knitted fabric (95% cotton and 5% elastane). This fabric is made and printed in Poland.

The comfy dress is designed for everyday use. It can fit a small petticoat and has 2 deep pockets <3, Of course, a petticoat is an option. You can wear this dress like a T-shirt and feel like a lazy sloth. Casual but cute.

The dress can be handwash in water. You can also use the washing machine, but a gentle program and warm water (30 Celsius degree).

This dress is a bit oversized, so if you don’t like this effect, please choose a smaller size. This type of fabric is elastic (5% elastane), so measurements can differ a bit.

title: "Rose Card" Onepiece Dress
description:
This series is produced by Misako Aoki. With a delicate spread of roses, white doves, postcards, this romantic collection showcases an antique world. This is a gorgeous dress with plenty of ruffles on the yoke. Delicate lace is added to the ruffled collar for a more elegant impression. Tucks are added to the sleeves and hem to add a classical accent.

The size can be adjusted with the matching string at the back of the waist. You can enjoy a silhouette to suit your preference. A lining was deliberately not added to make use of the light transparency. Combine with your favorite innerwear to enjoy a layered style. The fabric is made of delicate and airy silky voile. The light transparency creates a fleeting and beautiful appearance. 

Details:

  • Back buttons
  • Waist string for adjustments
  • Inside is not lined
  • Material: 100% polyester

title: Blue Meadow Dress
description:
The meadow dress is inspired by wildflowers scattered across an open field.  It has a flattering scoop neckline, an elastic waist, and pockets! 

This dress is elegant without being overly formal. It has vintage class, but is made entirely from comfortable, breathable cotton - including the lining! And of course, the pockets are very practical for any outing.

The waistband and sleeve cuffs are made with elastic for a soft and flattering fit. Designed with versatility in mind, the waist cinches and stretches to match your shape. title: Sweet Chocolate Journey Onepiece
description:
Ever dreamed of finding one of those Golden Tickets and having the chance of spending a day in Willy Wonka's World of Pure Imagination? With our Sweet Chocolate Journey collection you can!

The print features an enchanted candy land that has been inspired by Willy Wonka's chocolate room as well as the world of Disney's Sugar Rush. Wouldn't it be scrumdiddlyumptious to wander through the candy grass along that delicious chocolate river and try a bit of those marshmallow mushrooms, Fluffy T-Oreos, lollipops and swirly toffees while admiring the starry sky and that sugarcoated crescent moon?

This vintage-style OP dress with a Peter Pan collar has been inspired by that of darling little Veruca Salt from the original Willy Wonka movie. So, no guarantees, but chances are people might fulfill your every wish while you're wearing it, be it cream buns and donuts, a Golden Goose or a trained Squirrel. Like all of our dresses and skirts, it has practical pockets where you can keep your favourite candy, a pocket watch or anything else you might find useful during your journey.

Fluffy Tori strongly recommends to brush your teeth after wearing items from this collection. Or at least have some chewing gum.

Just not the blueberry-flavoured one. You have been warned...
